In order to compare the different trained ML models, two scoring techniques are introduced. For the regression of defect parameters, predictions are made on the validation dataset and correlated to the true defect parameter values. To score the correlation, the coefficient of determination (R2) is used51:5R2:=1−∑i=1N(yipred−yitrue)2∑i=1Nyitrue−ymeantrue2;\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
